00:01:04,370 --> 00:01:06,730
 May the deceased rest in peace. 

12
00:01:13,550 --> 00:01:15,730
What happened?

13
00:01:15,730 --> 00:01:19,050
They suddenly said he had terminal pancreatic cancer about a month ago.

14
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,340
You should've contacted me, then.

15
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:29,660
We're not close enough to contact each other, are we?

16
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:32,940
We're not. However...

17
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,910
He's Yu Ri's father.

18
00:01:37,910 --> 00:01:40,250
You should've let him say a farewell to his daughter, at least.

19
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:42,620
She can just say her farewell here, then.

20
00:01:42,620 --> 00:01:43,750
- What?
 - Hey!

21
00:01:43,750 --> 00:01:45,330
Hurry inside, say bye, and go.

22
00:01:45,330 --> 00:01:47,140
Don't talk to my daughter like that!

23
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:51,470
What are you doing here right now?

24
00:01:57,650 --> 00:01:59,620
Mom, it's fine.

25
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:01,640
Don't even bother. Let's go.

26
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:08,360
Say bye to Dad.

27
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:14,250
Why the heck are you doing this to me?

28
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:25,780
 He was punished for betraying us. 

29
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:39,250
 That day... 

30
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:44,570
 Dad's two women were crying 

31
00:02:45,130 --> 00:02:47,470
 for different reasons. 

32
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,800
Attorney Han?

33
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:59,080
 And here in this place... 

34
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:06,280
 there are two women once again. 

35
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:11,770
 Case 02: Two Women 

36
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:14,460
Attorney Cha!

37
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:32,200
 Why do these things keep happening to me? 

38
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,170
 Why on earth? 

39
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:37,030
You're still here?

40
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:41,930
I came to pick up the verdict.

41
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:45,610
Why did you come in at this hour, Attorney Cha?

42
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:49,880
I came to pick up the records, and the lights were on in your office.

43
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:55,150
I was so out of it for a while because of the case.

44
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:59,630
I toured the office while no one was here.

45
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:01,190
Sure.

46
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,040
Attorney Cha!

47
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:24,800
I'll get going from here.

48
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:27,220
Okay, I'll take the taxi a bit further ahead.

49
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,490
Okay.

50
00:04:28,490 --> 00:04:30,600
Please get home safely.

51
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,140
Take care.

